<p>The Description says that objects left in the portal are worn away after 5 minutes. It also says that propelled objects were obscured, until they had traveled to the distance about 3000&#160;km. It means that those objects had passed 3000&#160;km for less than 5 min, and their speed was to be minimum 3000&#160;km per 300 sec = 10km/second. That is equal to orbital velocity on Earth, so propelled object must be a space rockets launched inside the portal.</p>
